tissueExpression.summary: Moderate to strong cytoplasmic staining was observed in squamous epithelia, urothelium, glandular cells of epididymis and a small fraction of bone marrow cells. Remaining normal tissues were negative.

Moderate to strong cytoplasmic staining was observed in squamous epithelia, urothelium, glandular cells of epididymis and a small fraction of bone marrow cells. Remaining normal tissues were negative.
Moderate to strong cytoplasmic immunoreactivity was observed in several urothelial cancers and squamous cell carcinomas. Most other tumors were negative.
